meta.title: Nicole Han
meta.subtitle: Variety is the spice of life.
meta.description: I'm a gradute studying Computer Science at USC. I'm proficient in Java, Python, and Android Development. Previously, I worked on the Android team at Zillow and as an undergradute researcher with focus on Semantic analysis (machine learning) at The University of Hong Kong. Over the last few years I've developed apps and worked on projects such as CityTour and SmartLock. I am a big fan of traveling and I am super interested in the combination of traveling and technology!!!
meta.author: Nicole Han
